+	 * writes to RAM at full speed. The GPU accesses it through GART DMA,
+	 * which works through the PLX bridge's DMA path (proven by ring tests).
+	 *
+	 * This is the universal safety net — catches GEM_CREATE from X11/Mesa,
+	 * dumb_create from modetest, fbdev, and any other CPU access path.
